{"tid":1629092,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(行動)全香港人你地記得做好自己既位置","createTime":"2019-10-06T06:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:37:44.000Z","uid":186361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b08222daec8b7cfa839b9e5acb1ef7ec3ceb53d6","tid":1629092,"uid":186361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:33:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆 </span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">出核彈都唔會割 不捉鬼 </span></span></strong><br />\n<em>呢個絕對唔係單純口號 而係信念 <br />\n亦係對勇武既一種支持<br />\n</em><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">有時間就twitter解釋勇武做緊既野</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我相信大家都有有獨立思考<br />\n香港政府一而再 再而三咁打壓我地<br />\n我想問一句 我地冇做錯點解要驚班警察?<br />\n放假出街有罪? 用口罩就要驚警察拉你?<br />\n依家如果你仲驚港共政府佢地只會再加強打壓 完美令白色恐怖成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢篇野講得好好 請大家睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107762980595104/posts/136068031097932?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107762980595104%2Fposts%2F136068031097932%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lHr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=0e497cbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107762980595104/posts/136068031097932?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係勇武同和理非要做既野:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMYFOip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMYFOip.jpg&h=3b4965a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3NWmDq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3NWmDq.jpg&h=ce8b089d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8FdoRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8FdoRM.jpg&h=76e58584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QpBoL47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpBoL47.jpg&h=326985b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BqZ2hbO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqZ2hbO.jpg&h=74595fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共政府已經派大量<span style=\"color: blue;\">五毛</span><span style=\"color: red;\">三毛</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">左膠</span>潛入連登同TG 想令和理非同勇武割席 如果林奠係唔驚香港人就唔使做咁多小動作 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">千其唔好俾佢地帶到風向</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各自做好自己角色已經足夠</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地繼續一齊進步落去 更加團結</span></span><br />\n如果覺得講得岩就forward俾你朋友一齊推post"},{"pid":"2f4f87b400aee681b72e15030160017d21643050","tid":1629092,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2etZjqa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2etZjqa.jpg&h=8cdb81ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LcmPGDw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcmPGDw.jpg&h=1a05020d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff7149374a863a0515bf51f1abb7960464afd2dc","tid":1629092,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHK